==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Shipment
<hw>Ship"ment</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act
or process of shipping; <as>as, he was engaged in the <ex>shipment</ex>
of coal for London; an active <ex>shipment</ex> of wheat from the
West</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which is shipped.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The question is, whether the share of M. in the
<qex>shipment</qex> is exempted from condemnation by reason of his
neutral domicle.</q> <rj><qau>Story.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Shipowner</ent>⟦br⟧
